title: A Nightmare on Elm Street 8 Freddy Vs. Jason [FANEDIT]
description:
A Nightmare on Elm Street 8 Freddy Vs. Jason [Extended-Cut] BR 2017

I used the original Blursy source, and reinserted the Deleted footage from the Bluray special features also taking Alternate shot (Jason Goes To Hell) making it the longest Running Time. Enjoy 

Please leave feedback on my work Thanks
